This paper discusses the design and transmission of OTA signaling in cellular networks, which involves topics related to network infrastructure, information theory, communication systems, system and control theory, and multimedia. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.COMM (Communications and Networking), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
